# Testing Timelock and Governor
# Testing the Timelock

## Summary
The following vote tests the interaction from the timelock with arbitrary contracts.
It interacts with a simple [TestSwitchTimelock](https://etherscan.io/address/0x23Cf930DB556134E54E5a471694Ac05608DE5e0a#code) calling the `turnOn()` function which is accessible by anyone and `setArbitrary(bool)` which is only accessible by the Timelock (`0xdC554207e4EE62bB05AeC99b3D2C6ab2106D6442`)
